column5: Seen it before, but it's always worth another watch. What a great vid, and what a great memory for that kid!. The other kid, though, didn't seem overly thrilled....

Very cool, bet he'll be talking about that big fish for years to come.We have a kids Mickey Mouse rod/reel we use for friendly big fish competitions. Biggest anyone has ever boated with it was a 23" eye so far..
This video is for all us walleye fishing "experts" that buy the very best state of the art fishing tackle.https://www.wimp.com/little-boy-catc...nster-walleye/
